---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../../components/shared/Container.astro";
---

<Layout title="Website Ownership" description="Information about website ownership transfer options at Flores Nexus Group." lang="en" noindex={true}>
  <main class="pt-24 pb-20">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-heading-1 mb-6">Website Ownership</h1>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-heading-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            All Flores Nexus plans (Nexus Card, Starter Website, Professional Website) are <strong class="text-heading-1">managed services</strong>.
            This means Flores Nexus Group builds, hosts, maintains, and manages your website while your subscription is active.
          </p>

          <p>
            <strong class="text-heading-1">Ownership transfer is not included in any plan.</strong> It is a separate, optional service
            that is quoted based on the complexity of the project.
          </p>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-box-border bg-box-bg p-6">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading-1 mb-4">How Ownership Transfer Works</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">1.</span>
                You request a quote for ownership transfer.
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">2.</span>
                We evaluate the complexity of your website and provide a price (starting at $3,500).
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">3.</span>
                If approved, we prepare the files, documentation, and transfer process.
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">4.</span>
                You receive the complete website files and are responsible for hosting, maintenance, and updates going forward.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-300 dark:border-amber-700 bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/20 p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 mb-2">Important Notes</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300 text-sm">
              <li>• Most of our clients do not need ownership transfer because we handle everything.</li>
              <li>• After transfer, you are responsible for hosting, security, updates, and maintenance.</li>
              <li>• Domain transfer is a separate process with its own fees.</li>
              <li>• Ownership transfer does not include ongoing support after handoff.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <p>
            For questions about ownership transfer, contact us at{" "}
            <a href="mailto:hola@floresnexus.com" class="text-primary hover:underline font-semibold">hola@floresnexus.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </main>
</Layout>
